Package jetbrains.mps.openapi.editor.menus

Interface EditorMenuDescriptor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditorMenuDescriptorBase
    public interface EditorMenuDescriptor
    The descriptor of the editor menu part. Used for representing the editor menu trace.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      String getDescription()
      Text description of the editor menu part
      org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.model.SNodeReference getSource()
      Reference to the node which is the source of the menu part
      boolean isImplicit()
      If the menu part doesn't have the source node or its source node is not stored in the editor model (e.g the source node is the annotation on the concept declaration which produces the menu part on the generation time) then the menu part is considered as implicit.
